 refugees\n*[[Refugee Radio]]\n* [[Refugee Studies Centre]]\n* [[Refugees United]]\n* [[Refugee Olympic Athletes at the 2016 Summer Olympics]]\n* [[Right of asylum]]\n* [[The I Live Here Projects]], a nonprofit storytelling organization\n* [[Refugee children]] and [[refugee women]]\n* [[Refugee Nation]]\n* [[Third country resettlement]]\n\n{{Div col end}}\n\n==Footnotes==\n{{notelist-ua|30em}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n===Works cited===\n{{Refbegin |60em}}\n* {{cite encyclopedia |last=Aggrawal |first=A. |title=Refugee Medicine |year=2005 |pages=514\u2013525 |veditors=Payne-James JJ, Byard RW, Corey TS, Henderson C |encyclopedia=Encyclopedia of Forensic and Legal Medicine |publisher=Elsevier Academic Press |location=London |volume=3|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |author=Assembly of Heads of State and Government (Sixth Ordinary Session) |title=OAU convention governing the specific aspects of refugee problems in Africa |date=September 1969 |url=http://www.unhcr.org/about-us/background/45dc1a682/oau-convention-governing-specific-aspects-refugee-problems-africa-adopted.html |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last1=Bassel |first1=Leah |title=Refugee Women: Beyond Gender Versus Culture |date=2012|ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |title=Cartagena Declaration on Refugees |url=http://www.unhcr.org/about-us/background/45dc19084/cartagena-declaration-refugees-adopted-colloquium-international-protection.html |ref=CITEREFCartagena Declaration}}\n* {{citation |title=Convention and Protocol relating to the Status of Refugees |year=1967 |page= |url=http://www.unhcr.org/protect/PROTECTION/3b66c2aa10.pdf |volume= |publisher=Office of the United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees (UNHCR), Communications and Public Information Service |location=Geneva, Switzerland |language= |isbn=|ref=CITEREFConvention Protocol relating1967}}\n* {{cite web |title=Convention relating to the Status of Refugees |url=http://www.ohchr.org/EN/ProfessionalInterest/Pages/StatusOfRefugees.aspx |website=www.ohchr.org |a